211
00:14:30,050 --> 00:14:31,800
Nhóm Hinata đi chạy rồi.

212
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,270
Yamaguchi-kun không đi theo à?

213
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:37,590
